s/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油呀絲打 如果大家真係the right one<br />\n咩風浪都唔會怕 <br />\n其實個男仔都會好掛住你<br />\n大家都要俾多啲安全感對方 咩都自己講<br />\n多啲FaceTime <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一年好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92acb950265bae120ea4679abc3f8181c9514e52","tid":393790,"uid":81435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:54:51.000Z","msg":"Long d 左半年 最近開始嘈交 一嘈我就訓唔到等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8ae4a159ebe92f062a04af56f9e965d48ee381","tid":393790,"uid":20560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:03:34.000Z","msg":"拍拖5年 long左3年 出年6月完<br />\n利申今時今日都仲係熱戀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa197abb4ec080a1eb588e695e68698849de70e7","tid":393790,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"long d散咗幾年,最近一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但差唔多又開sem又要番去啦<br />\n好無安全感<br />\n好怕我番咗過去佢又唔理我<br />\n好怕同之前一樣咁散法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我啲朋友因為佢之前咁對我所以唔係幾中意佢,宜家真係唔知可以同邊個講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好驚好驚....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5254318181d2c4933989e9c64b73fd5193ced595","tid":393790,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍拖5年 long左3年 出年6月完<br />\n利申今時今日都仲係熱戀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdeece9940613196aff829867fd6048f2a93e8f2","tid":393790,"uid":55683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>long d緊 岩岩一個星期<br />\n好掛住你阿男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油呀絲打 如果大家真係the right one<br />\n咩風浪都唔會怕 <br />\n其實個男仔都會好掛住你<br />\n大家都要俾多啲安全感對方 咩都自己講<br />\n多啲FaceTime <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一年好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地都係初戀 <br />\n日日都好掛住對方 <br />\n不過就冇FaceTime啦 日日一齊打機 幾忙都抽時間出黎同對方傾計 同朋友出去唔得閒會提早報備咁 其實冇野驚<br />\n聖誕節有得返去見佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e8566e9c9df82ec97bff8a58630a32c1874b9b","tid":393790,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"點挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地兩個都係今年FG<br />\n不過佢去外國進修一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一諗起返工唔開心<br />\n收工無人同我傾訴<br />\n返工無咩目標去令我期待放假<br />\n諗下都難挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861521ef1db328804e3eb0b4d997f1dfb22df098","tid":393790,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地兩個都係今年FG<br />\n不過佢去外國進修一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一諗起返工唔開心<br />\n收工無人同我傾訴<br />\n返工無咩目標去令我期待放假<br />\n諗下都難挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都有whatsapp facetime架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好用個挨字"},{"pid":"cb1ffcc688f6bf20d1ee12f5a56d3b95c37c0a1c","tid":393790,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"已捱過一年<br />\n仲有兩年<br />\n準備損手爛腳<br />\n希望唔洗<im